  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4888461/" class="title-link">突如其来的第三空间</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4888461"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/12036924/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u12036924-79.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/12036924/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">紫檀</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-04-02"
      class="main-meta">2011-04-02 00:24:07</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4888461_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  读完这本书，突然有种身处世外的感觉。笛卡尔发明了坐标，解开了“提洛秘题”，说出了“我思故我在”，然后还有F+V-E=2。正如作者在序言里描述的，GPRS在现今世界的广泛应用，也要归功于笛卡尔，而F+V-E=2更是为后世开启了第三空间的一扇窗户

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4888461_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4888461_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
